<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Pokemon app</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div id="app"></div>

    <script src="bundle.js"></script>

</body>
</html>

html,
body,
#app {
    height: 100%;
}

.container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 100%;
}

main,
footer {
    padding: 0 20px;
}

main {
    flex-grow: 1;
    background-color: azure;
}

footer {
    line-height: 3em;
}

.pokemon-small {
    overflow: hidden;
}
.pokemon-small img {
    width: 50px;
    transform: scale(2);
    padding: 0 5px;
}

.pokemon-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    min-height: 116px;
    margin: 20px auto;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: 1px solid lightslategrey;
    border-radius: 20px;
}

.pokemon-container img {
    float: left;
    padding-right: 20px;
}

.pokemon-container h5 {
    text-transform: capitalize;
}
